		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You whisper a spell that shields you from being detected from your target, damaging their mind in the process.</em></p><p><strong>Intelligence Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 2d6 psychic]] damage and is &amp;reference[charmed]. While charmed in this way, your target is unable to see you or otherwise detect your presence. Target rolls save again at the end of each of their turns, ending effect on success.</p><p>The effect ends if you take hostile action against the target.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 1st.</p>",
